---
import Author from '../Author.astro';
---

<div class='about-the-author'>
	<h3 class='section-label'>// About Hanif</h3>
	<Author picSize='md' />
	<div class='author-desc mt-4 space-y-3 text-[0.95rem] leading-7 text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300'>
		<p class='mb-3'>
			Hanif builds MVPs, workflow automation, and useful AI systems for nontechnical founders and founder-led teams. Based in Buenos Aires, he helps clients narrow the first useful version, ship it, and leave with software their team can own.
		</p>
		<p>His main stack is TypeScript, React, Next.js, and Node.js. He is currently available for roadmap calls and focused build engagements.</p>
	</div>
</div>
